Request for postman:

1. Create reader:
    http://localhost:8080/api/library/createReader

    body:
            {
                "name": "Piotr",
                "surname": "Szczepanski"
            }

2. Get all readers:
    http://localhost:8080/api/library/getReaders

3. get reader by Id:
    http://localhost:8080/api/library/getReaderById?readerId=19

4. get reader by name and surname:
    http://localhost:8080/api/library/getReader?name=Piotr&&surname=Szczepanski

5. delete reader by Id:
    http://localhost:8080/api/library/deleteReaderById?readerId=16

6. delete reader by name and surname:
    http://localhost:8080/api/library/deleteReaderByNameAndSurname?name=Piotr&&surname=Szczepanski



